Revision history for Net-Prometheus-PerlCollector

0.03    2020-05-12
        [CHANGES]
         * Report a platform info metric containing the Perl interpreter
           version

        [BUGFIXES]
         * Fix off-by-one in stack EXTEND() logic in XS function

0.02    2020-05-01
        [CHANGES]
         * Optionally collect more detail about SVs classifying by type or
           blessed class
         * Use `perl_collector_detail` collector param to set level of detail

0.01    2018-10-11 18:08:48
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
